    <chapter title="So... You want to Contribute?" id="so-you-want-to-contribute">
        <p>First of all... Thank you! I always welcome contributions to open issues or features you would like to see in a Project I maintain.</p>
        <p>All types of contributions are encouraged and valued. See the Table of Contents (left menu) for different ways to help and details about how we handle them. Please make sure to read the relevant section before making your contribution. It will make it a lot easier for us maintainers and smooth out the experience for all involved. Our community looks forward to your contributions.</p>
        <p>Enjoy a Project, but just don't have the time needed to contribute? That's fine! There are other ways you can help show us your support.</p>
        <list>
            <li>Add a Star to a Project.</li>
            <li>Post about a Project to Social Media.</li>
            <li>Link the Project in your README if you leverage it.</li>
            <li>Share the Project by Word of Mouth. Reference it in a Relevant Context if it may help someone else.</li>
        </list>
    </chapter>

